"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-olympics-2024-taylor-swift-simone-biles-b2591165.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Olympics promo was set to one of Swift's hit songs, 'Style'  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999993032104312, \"rank\": 6.870885108808023e-07, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Taylor Swiftsaluted Team USA starsSimone Biles,Sha'Carri Richardson, andKatie Ledeckyin a new video for theParis 2024Olympics.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9848071254358743, \"rank\": 0.015426592364561266, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 34-year-old singernarrated a promo for the NBC Primetime Olympicswhich aired on August 3.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.999233425800414, \"rank\": 0.0007671548585198109, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unsurprisingly, the ad featured one of Swift's hit songs, \\\"Style,\\\" from her re-released album,1989.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999993032104312, \"rank\": 6.870885108808023e-07, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video included shots from this year's Games including Biles on the mat and Richardson on the track.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999990291144, \"rank\": 9.709550730843415e-10, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never be afraid to show them who you are,\\\" Swift says in a voiceover.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Especially when the whole world is watching.\\\"\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The promo also featured a video of Ledecky diving into a swimming pool during an Olympic event.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because there is no one way to be the best.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No one way to inspire everyone else who will someday follow,\\\" Swift continued.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The promo went on to pay tribute to the American athletes with one shot of Biles waving at the crowd, after doing an impressive flip on the mat, and another of Richardson giving a fan a high-five.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9989843364467049, \"rank\": 0.0010119670234806143, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1339, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999990291144, \"rank\": 9.709550730843415e-10, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do what you love.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You love what you do,\\\" Swift said.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her song went on to play, with her singing: \\\"We never go out of style.\\\"\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift's moving message then referenced her song, as she said: \\\"Believe in your style.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whatever it is.\\\"\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The video continued with shots of Ledecky cheering in the pool, Biles smiling on the mat, and\\u00a0Richardson showing off her long, painted nails for the camera.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999990291144, \"rank\": 9.709550730843415e-10, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Grammy-Award winner then gave a sweet shout-out to each of these Olympians.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Katie, Sha'Carri, and Simone, three American stars, three different visions of greatness,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The promos is a dedication to three of the most successful US atheletes in the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.9965736612047149, \"rank\": 0.0034255447375460516, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has 10 Olympic medals so far, as she won three of her gold ones during this year's Olympics.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Ledecky has more than 14 Olympic medals, four of which she won during this year's Olympics.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the the women's 100-meter final on August 3, Richardson took home the silver, marking the fan-favorite's first-ever Olympic medal win.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999999990291144, \"rank\": 9.709550730843415e-10, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not the first time that Swift has honored US Olympians, and has close ties with Biles.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999993032104312, \"rank\": 6.870885108808023e-07, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}, {\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.9965736612047149, \"rank\": 0.0034255447375460516, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the 2024 US Olympic Gymnastic Trials on June 27, Biles competed in the qualifiers with anincredible floor routineset to Swift's 2017 song: \\\"...Ready For It?\\\"\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"score\": 0.9999993032104312, \"rank\": 6.870885108808023e-07, \"text\": \"Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 29, Swiftresponded to the gymnastics legendby reposting avideoof her floor routine to X.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Watched this so many times and still unready.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's ready for it tho,\\\" Swift posted.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Biles withdrew from the Tokyo Olympics in July 2021,\\u00a0due to her mental health, Swiftshowed her support in a moving video tribute for the gymnast.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the singer narrated theclip, set to her 2020 song \\\"This Is Me Trying,\\\" she acknowledged the public scrutiny that Biles faced.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What do we want from our heroes?\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we expect of them?\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do we need from them?\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What happens when they surprise us?\\\"\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swift said.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you have the attention of the world, everything you do takes on a bigger meaning.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be a heavy burden.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can be a chance to change everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles respondedto the message from Swift on Xat the time, writing: \\\"I am crying.\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How special.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love you Taylor Swift.\\\"\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8134434275648556e-41, \"text\": \"Taylor Swift\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Swift\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singer then replied: \\\"I cried watching YOU.\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel so lucky to have gotten to watch you all these years, but this week was a lesson in emotional intelligence and resilience.\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We all learned from you.\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you.\\\"\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3808, \"end\": 3819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8248559717733655e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"